{"tid":2058473,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃黑旗同香港唔襯，整咗支代表東亞自由堡壘嘅旗","createTime":"2020-06-10T07:48:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-10T10:23:45.000Z","uid":155522,"like":10,"dislike":354,"uniUserReply":60,"replies":[{"pid":"5636d9a1f4568cbb8b925184836594589556cce7","tid":2058473,"uid":155522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T07:48:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RxfAmJe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRxfAmJe.jpg&h=542bb340&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NNcvaBE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNNcvaBE.jpg&h=7e9025bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/akx7cP3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fakx7cP3.jpg&h=cd81bc74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個 friend 認為黃黑旗始終冇香港嘅感覺，佢半膠半認真整咗支香港旗<br />\n<br />\n「係呢支旗入面可以睇到香港嘅 heritage, 亦都睇到現時抗爭嘅元素,<br />\n<br />\n最重要嘅係我想打造好似北歐各個國家嘅國旗家族 (佢哋係十字, google Nordic flags),<br />\n<br />\n但係呢個國旗家族係東亞自由民主國嘅國旗家族 (白色底, 中心圓)<br />\n<br />\n就算唔攞嚟做主要抗爭嘅旗幟可以攞嚟 connect 下東亞日韓」<br />\n<br />\n（實驗製品, 有好評再微調）"},{"pid":"74f807a9f4295301dd92b7b75ea7fa0c9bf71180","tid":2058473,"uid":155522,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T07:58:03.000Z","msg":"不喜請細力D屌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fcf7e99ad98db0f9dc812d97636c2fce5a36681","tid":2058473,"uid":35924,"like":81,"dislike":2,"score":79,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T08:00:21.000Z","msg":"真心唔掂，直接加d 字上去係想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0be4f3ed767e4774bfcb39ef5329b9b3b4a496a6","tid":2058473,"uid":48083,"like":22,"dislike":15,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T08:00:47.000Z","msg":"認同黃黑旗唔襯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a85e9fdcecc23e564774a0acfdad1eee305c085","tid":2058473,"uid":11698,"like":2,"dislike"